INTJ.title: Architect
INTJ.description: Independent and analytical strategist. Has high standards and a clear vision, valuing efficiency.
INTJ.loveStyle: Seeks deep and meaningful relationships, attracted to a partner's intellectual side. Shows love through actions rather than words.

INTP.title: Logician
INTP.description: Curious thinker. Interested in logic and theory, enjoys analyzing complex problems.
INTP.loveStyle: Values intellectual connection, wants a partner to discuss and share ideas with.

ENTJ.title: Commander
ENTJ.description: Natural leader. Confident and decisive, moves efficiently toward goals.
ENTJ.loveStyle: Values growing and achieving goals together with a partner. Expresses affection directly.

ENTP.title: Debater
ENTP.description: Creative idea bank. Enjoys exploring new possibilities and debating.
ENTP.loveStyle: Wants a fun and stimulating relationship. Loves intellectual conversations and new experiences together.

INFJ.title: Advocate
INFJ.description: Idealistic helper. Uses deep insight to understand and help others.
INFJ.loveStyle: Seeks a soulmate. Values deep and meaningful emotional connections.

INFP.title: Mediator
INFP.description: Emotional idealist. Has personal values and pursues an authentic life.
INFP.loveStyle: Dreams of true love. Wants to understand a partner's inner world and form deep emotional bonds.

ENFJ.title: Protagonist
ENFJ.description: Charismatic leader. Loves discovering and nurturing others' potential.
ENFJ.loveStyle: Devoted and romantic. Helps partner grow and pursues deep emotional connection.

ENFP.title: Campaigner
ENFP.description: Passionate free spirit. Sees possibilities and loves inspiring others.
ENFP.loveStyle: Loves authentically and passionately. Wants to share new experiences and grow together.

ISTJ.title: Logistician
ISTJ.description: Reliable person in charge. Systematic and thorough, sees tasks through to completion.
ISTJ.loveStyle: Serious and devoted. Shows love through actions rather than words, seeks stable relationships.

ISFJ.title: Defender
ISFJ.description: Warm protector. Devotedly cares for and protects loved ones.
ISFJ.loveStyle: Loves quietly but deeply. Cares attentively and wants to build a stable home.

ESTJ.title: Executive
ESTJ.description: Organized manager. Values order and systems, handles tasks efficiently.
ESTJ.loveStyle: Responsible and devoted. Values traditional values and seeks stable relationships.

ESFJ.title: Consul
ESFJ.description: Social caretaker. Enjoys identifying and meeting others' needs.
ESFJ.loveStyle: Warm and devoted. Cares for partner attentively and pursues harmonious relationships.

ISTP.title: Virtuoso
ISTP.description: Practical problem solver. Logical and realistic, solves problems hands-on.
ISTP.loveStyle: Wants a free and independent relationship. Shows love through actions rather than words.

ISFP.title: Adventurer
ISFP.description: Gentle artist. Enjoys the present and experiences the world in their own way.
ISFP.loveStyle: Loves quietly but deeply. Treasures every moment spent together.

ESTP.title: Entrepreneur
ESTP.description: Active problem solver. Realistic and action-oriented, enjoys spontaneous situations.
ESTP.loveStyle: Wants a fun and lively relationship. Loves experiencing new things together.

ESFP.title: Entertainer
ESFP.description: Spontaneous entertainer. Enjoys socializing and living in the moment.
ESFP.loveStyle: Fun and affectionate. Loves sharing enjoyable experiences together.
